<lb n="0296a21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0296a2101" cb:type="dharani"><note n="0296034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唵＋（引一）夾註【明】【丁】，〔唵〕－【聖】</note><app n="0296034"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丁】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0296035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">虐虐＝虎虎【丙】</note><app n="0296035"><lem wit="【大】">虐虐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">虎虎</rdg></app>吽娑<note n="0296036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚩＝縛【聖】</note><app n="0296036"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合<note n="0296037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0296037"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note><note n="0296038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">賀＋（引二）夾註【明】，（引）夾註【聖】，（引一）夾註【丁】</note><app n="0296038"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">賀<note place="inline">引二</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】">賀<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0296a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0296a2201">若欲作此天法。先須<note n="0296039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">畫＝造【聖】</note><app n="0296039"><lem wit="【大】">畫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">造</rdg></app>像。或用<note n="0296040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">白＝曰【聖】</note><app n="0296040"><lem wit="【大】">白</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">曰</rdg></app>鑞<note n="0296041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">銅＝錭【聖】</note><app n="0296041"><lem wit="【大】">銅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">錭</rdg></app>木
<lb n="0296a23" ed="T"/>等及花木。若鑄若刻並得。其像形。夫婦二身
<lb n="0296a24" ed="T"/><note n="0296042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">令＝合【乙】</note><app n="0296042"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">合</rdg></app>相抱立。<note n="0296043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">各長＝長各【丙】</note><app n="0296043"><lem wit="【大】">各長</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">長各</rdg></app>五寸。或七寸皆得。並作象
<lb n="0296a25" ed="T"/>頭人身。造像不得<note n="0296044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">違＝還【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】＊</note><app n="0296044"><lem wit="【大】">違</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">還</rdg></app><note n="0296045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">價＝像【乙】</note><app n="0296045"><lem wit="【大】">價</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">像</rdg></app>。<note n="0296046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（造）＋其【聖】</note><app n="0296046"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">造其</rdg></app>像<note n="0296047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">成已＝或【丙】</note><app n="0296047"><lem wit="【大】">成<note n="0296048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔已〕－【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0296048"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">或</rdg></app>。當
<lb n="0296a26" ed="T"/>以白月一日。於淨室內。用淨牛糞摩作圓壇。
<lb n="0296a27" ed="T"/>隨<note n="0296049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">意＝心【聖】</note><app n="0296049"><lem wit="【大】">意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">心</rdg></app>大小。當取一升清<note n="0296050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔細〕－【明】，細＝淨胡【聖】【乙】，油【甲】，胡【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0296050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔細〕－【明】，細＝淨胡【聖】【乙】，＝油【甲】，＝胡【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0296050"><lem wit="【大】">細</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【乙】">淨胡</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">油</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】">胡</rdg></app>麻油。<note n="0296051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔以〕－【聖】</note><app n="0296051"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0296052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">淨＋（一）【丙】</note><app n="0296052"><lem wit="【大】">淨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">淨一</rdg></app>銅
<lb n="0296a28" ed="T"/>器盛之。用上呪<note n="0296053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔文〕－【丙】</note><app n="0296053"><lem wit="【大】">文</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>呪油一百八遍。即<note n="0296054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">暖＝煖【明】【聖】</note><app n="0296054"><lem wit="【大】">暖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】">煖</rdg></app>其
<lb n="0296a29" ed="T"/>油。然後將像放著油中。安置壇內。用淨銅
<pb n="0296b" xml:id="T21.1266.0296b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0296b01" ed="T"/><note n="0296055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">匙＝起【聖】</note><app n="0296055"><lem wit="【大】">匙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">起</rdg></app>銅杓等率油。灌其二像頂身一百八遍。一
<lb n="0296b02" ed="T"/>日之中七遍灌之。平曉四遍日<note n="0296056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">午＝子【聖】，中【乙】</note><note n="0296056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">午＝子【聖】，＝中【乙】</note><app n="0296056"><lem wit="【大】">午</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">子</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">中</rdg></app>三遍共成
<lb n="0296b03" ed="T"/>七遍。已後每日更呪舊油以灌其像。如是作
<lb n="0296b04" ed="T"/>法乃至七日。隨心所願即得稱意。正灌油之
<lb n="0296b05" ed="T"/>時數<note n="0296057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔數〕－【丙】</note><app n="0296057"><lem wit="【大】">數</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>發願。復用<note n="0296058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">酥＝蘇【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0296058"><lem wit="【大】">酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】【乙】">蘇</rdg></app>蜜和<g ref="#CB00595"/>作團。及蘿蔔
<lb n="0296b06" ed="T"/>根并一盞酒。及歡喜團時新花菓等。如是日
<lb n="0296b07" ed="T"/>別取新者供養。一切善事隨<note n="0296059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">意＝願【明】【丁】</note><app n="0296059"><lem wit="【大】">意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丁】">願</rdg></app>成就。一切災
<lb n="0296b08" ed="T"/><note n="0296060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">禍＝難【乙】</note><app n="0296060"><lem wit="【大】">禍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">難</rdg></app><note n="0296061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悉皆＝皆悉【乙】</note><app n="0296061"><lem wit="【大】">悉皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">皆悉</rdg></app><note n="0296062" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">銷＝消【明】【聖】【乙】【丁】</note><app n="0296062"><lem wit="【大】">銷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【乙】【丁】">消</rdg></app>滅。其所獻食必須<note n="0296063" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自＋（身）【乙】</note><app n="0296063"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">自身</rdg></app>食始得
<lb n="0296b09" ed="T"/>氣<note n="0296064" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">力＋（得靈驗故行者可用之也）【乙】</note><app n="0296064"><lem wit="【大】">力</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">力得靈驗故行者可用之也</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0296b10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0296b1001">請召<note n="0296065" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">印＋（呪）【明】【聖】【甲】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0296065"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【丙】【丁】">印呪</rdg></app>。以二小指<note n="0296066" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二〕－【聖】</note><app n="0296066"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>無名指。相鉤向內。即
<lb n="0296b11" ed="T"/>以二中指竪相叉。<note n="0296067" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">又＝復【乙】</note><app n="0296067"><lem wit="【大】">又</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">復</rdg></app>以<note n="0296068" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二〕－【甲】</note><app n="0296068"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>頭指。各竪附中
<lb n="0296b12" ed="T"/>指。以二大指亦竪。附近頭指側。大指來去。</p>
<lb n="0296b13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0296b1301">呪曰。</p>
