<lb n="0296b18" ed="T"/><note n="0296078" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">底＋（三）夾註【明】【丁】</note><app n="0296078"><lem wit="【大】">底</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丁】">底<note place="inline">三</note></rdg></app>摩賀誐娜簸底<note n="0296079" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（扇底迦羅野）＋娑ィ【丁】</note><app n="0296079"><lem wit="【大】">娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】" type="variantRemark">扇底迦羅野娑</rdg></app>嚩<note place="inline">二合<app type="star" corresp="#0296029"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>賀<note n="0296080" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引＋（四）【明】【丁】，〔引〕－【聖】</note><app n="0296080"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丁】"><note place="inline">引四</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
