<lb n="0296b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0296b2501">若欲作法時。先以上呪呪水七遍。用洗口。
<lb n="0296b26" ed="T"/><note n="0296093" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">并＝合【丙】</note><app n="0296093"><lem wit="【大】">并</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">合</rdg></app>更取水<note n="0296094" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔呪〕－【聖】</note><app n="0296094"><lem wit="【大】">呪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>七遍。用楊柳散灑身上即為
<lb n="0296b27" ed="T"/>護身。然後入<note n="0296095" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">持誦＝誦持【明】</note><app n="0296095"><lem wit="【大】">持誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">誦持</rdg></app>室中作法之所。</p>
<lb n="0296b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0296b2801">洗浴<app type="star" corresp="#0296074"><lem wit="【大】">呪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">呪曰</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0296b29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0296b2901" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0296031"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丁】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>阿拏<note n="0296096" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婆＝娑【明】【丁】</note><app n="0296096"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丁】">娑</rdg></app>折<note n="0296097" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唎＝利【乙】</note><app n="0296097"><lem wit="【大】">唎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">利</rdg></app><note n="0296098" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合〕－【聖】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0296098"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>婆<note n="0296099" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">跛＝跋【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0296099"><lem wit="【大】">跛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】">跋</rdg></app>隷拏<note n="0296100" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＋（二）夾註【明】【丁】，（吽）【乙】</note><app n="0296100"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丁】">訶<note place="inline">二</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">訶吽</rdg></app></p>
<pb n="0296c" xml:id="T21.1266.0296c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0296c01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0296c0101">以上呪呪水七遍當用洗浴。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0296c02" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="2" type="其他">調和毘那夜迦法</cb:mulu><head><note n="0296101" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">調＝誦【聖】</note><app n="0296101"><lem wit="【大】">調</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">誦</rdg></app>和毘那夜迦法</head>
<lb n="0296c03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0296c0301"><note n="0296102" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（先須）＋請【乙】</note><app n="0296102"><lem wit="【大】">請</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">先須請</rdg></app>一切天作帝殊<note n="0296103" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">羅＝囉【明】＊</note><app n="0296103"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">囉</rdg></app>施印。以二小指無名
<lb n="0296c04" ed="T"/>指。相叉於掌內。竪二中指<note n="0296104" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔指〕－【聖】【甲】【丙】＊</note><app n="0296104"><lem wit="【大】">指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>頭相捻。以
<lb n="0296c05" ed="T"/><note n="0296105" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二〕－【明】【丁】</note><app n="0296105"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>頭指各加中指背第一節下半<note n="0296106" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">分＋（以）【乙】</note><app n="0296106"><lem wit="【大】">分</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">分以</rdg></app>。大<app type="star" corresp="#0296104"><lem wit="【大】">指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0296c06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0296c0601"><note n="0296107" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">來去＝則去來【乙】</note><app n="0296107"><lem wit="【大】">來去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">則去來</rdg></app>呪曰。</p>
<pb n="0297a" xml:id="T21.1266.0297a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0297a01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0297a0101" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline"><note n="0297001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（引）＋一【明】【丁】</note><app n="0297001"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丁】">引一</rdg></app></note>鑠都<note n="0297002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚕＝魯【聖】</note><app n="0297002"><lem wit="【大】">嚕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">魯</rdg></app><note place="inline">二</note><note n="0297003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">波＝婆【乙】</note><app n="0297003"><lem wit="【大】">波</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">婆</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0296103"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">囉</rdg></app>摩馱儞曳<note place="inline">三</note><note n="0297004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">莎＝娑【明】【聖】，莎訶＝娑羅二合賀四【乙】</note><note n="0297004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">莎訶＝娑羅二合賀四【乙】，莎＝娑【明】【聖】</note><app n="0297004"><lem wit="【大】">莎<note n="0297005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＋（引四）夾註【明】【丁】，（四）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0297005"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丁】">訶<note place="inline">引四</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">訶<note place="inline">四</note></rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">娑羅二合賀四</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】">娑訶</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0297a02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0297a0201"><app type="star" corresp="#0296087"><lem wit="【大】">誦七遍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。但是誦呪人夢中驚怖。見諸畜生惡
<lb n="0297a03" ed="T"/>境界等。當知是毘那夜迦王瞋。夢中覺已即
<lb n="0297a04" ed="T"/>慚愧乞<note n="0297006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">莫＝真【聖】</note><app n="0297006"><lem wit="【大】">莫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">真</rdg></app>瞋。明日自有飲食勞謝。以水摩地
<lb n="0297a05" ed="T"/>作二肘<note n="0297007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">水＝小【丙】</note><app n="0297007"><lem wit="【大】">水</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">小</rdg></app>圓壇。如<note n="0297008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">槃＝盤【聖】【丙】</note><app n="0297008"><lem wit="【大】">槃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【丙】">盤</rdg></app>大亦得。即取<note n="0297009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">𩟘＝烝【明】，<g ref="#CB14650"/>【聖】，蒸【丁】</note><note n="0297009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𩟘＝烝【明】，＝<g ref="#CB14650"/>【聖】，＝蒸【丁】</note><app n="0297009"><lem wit="【大】">𩟘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">烝</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><g ref="#CB14650"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】">蒸</rdg></app>餅五
<lb n="0297a06" ed="T"/>顆蘿蔔根三顆火燒<note n="0297010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">熟＝就【聖】</note><app n="0297010"><lem wit="【大】">熟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">就</rdg></app>。有花著<note n="0297011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">花＋（者）【丙】</note><app n="0297011"><lem wit="【大】">花</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">花者</rdg></app>并燒<note n="0297012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">白＝內【聖】</note><app n="0297012"><lem wit="【大】">白</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">內</rdg></app>
<lb n="0297a07" ed="T"/>膠薰陸等香安於壇中。呪人<note n="0297013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔壇〕－【乙】</note><app n="0297013"><lem wit="【大】">壇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0297014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">西面＝面西【聖】</note><app n="0297014"><lem wit="【大】">西面</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">面西</rdg></app>向東
<lb n="0297a08" ed="T"/>坐。誦大自在天呪一百八遍已。口云慚愧好
<lb n="0297a09" ed="T"/>去。如是語已。壇中雜物<note n="0297015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">盤＝槃【甲】</note><app n="0297015"><lem wit="【大】">盤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">槃</rdg></app><note n="0297016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">盛＝出【聖】</note><app n="0297016"><lem wit="【大】">盛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">出</rdg></app>。出門向西棄
<lb n="0297a10" ed="T"/>却。西北亦得。口云薩婆藥叉<note n="0297017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＋（剎）【乙】</note><app n="0297017"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">囉剎</rdg></app>闍阿藹捨
<lb n="0297a11" ed="T"/>訶<note n="0297018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娑＝婆【乙】</note><app n="0297018"><lem wit="【大】">娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">婆</rdg></app>鉢闍伽車。作是語<note n="0297019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔已〕－【聖】</note><app n="0297019"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>棄却即<note n="0297020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">歸＝婦【聖】，得【丙】</note><note n="0297020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">歸＝婦【聖】，＝得【丙】</note><app n="0297020"><lem wit="【大】">歸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">婦</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">得</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0297a12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0297a1201">大自在天呪<note n="0297021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔曰〕－【明】【甲】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0297021"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0297a13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0297a1301" cb:type="dharani">唵<note n="0297022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（引）＋一【明】【丁】，〔一〕－【聖】</note><app n="0297022"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丁】"><note place="inline">引一</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>毘<note n="0297023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">跢＝哆【明】</note><app n="0297023"><lem wit="【大】">跢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">哆</rdg></app>囉薩尼<note place="inline">二</note><note n="0297024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">波＝婆【聖】</note><app n="0297024"><lem wit="【大】">波</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">婆</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0296022"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">羅</rdg></app><note n="0297025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">末＝未【聖】</note><app n="0297025"><lem wit="【大】">末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">未</rdg></app>唎達尼<note place="inline">三</note>瞋
<lb n="0297a14" ed="T"/>達尼瞋達<note n="0297026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔尼〕－【聖】</note><app n="0297026"><lem wit="【大】">尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note place="inline">四</note>頻達尼頻達尼<note n="0297027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔五〕－【聖】</note><app n="0297027"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">五</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0297028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">莎＝婆【明】，娑【聖】【丁】，莎訶＝娑嚩二合賀引【乙】</note><note n="0297028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">莎訶＝娑嚩二合賀引【乙】，莎＝婆【明】，莎＝娑【聖】【丁】</note><app n="0297028"><lem wit="【大】">莎<note n="0297029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＋（六）夾註【明】【甲】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0297029"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【丙】【丁】">訶<note place="inline">六</note></rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">娑嚩二合賀引</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">婆訶</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【丁】">娑訶</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0297a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0297a1501">誦呪一百八遍。即心歡喜非但夢中。但覺有
<lb n="0297a16" ed="T"/><note n="0297030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">魔＝鬼【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0297030"><lem wit="【大】">魔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】【乙】">鬼</rdg></app>事即作前法定<note n="0297031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">好＋（也）【乙】</note><app n="0297031"><lem wit="【大】">好</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">好也</rdg></app>。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0297a17" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="3" type="其他">造像法</cb:mulu><head><note n="0297032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">造像法＝造聖天像法【乙】</note><app n="0297032"><lem wit="【大】">造像法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">造聖天像法</rdg></app></head>
<lb n="0297a18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0297a1801">其像形端立。象頭人身。左牙出右牙折。面少
<lb n="0297a19" ed="T"/>向左。其鼻向外<note n="0297033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">瘻＝僂【明】</note><app n="0297033"><lem wit="【大】">瘻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">僂</rdg></app>。有六臂。其左上手把刀。
<lb n="0297a20" ed="T"/>次手把果盤。下手把輪。右上手把棒。次手把
<lb n="0297a21" ed="T"/>索。下手把牙。造此<note n="0297034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">像＝象【明】</note><app n="0297034"><lem wit="【大】">像</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">象</rdg></app>不得<app type="star" corresp="#0296044"><lem wit="【大】">違</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">還</rdg></app>價。足數付之。
<lb n="0297a22" ed="T"/>若鑄<note n="0297035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔若刻〕－【聖】</note><app n="0297035"><lem wit="【大】">若刻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>若<note n="0297036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">畫＝盡【聖】</note><app n="0297036"><lem wit="【大】">畫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">盡</rdg></app>並得。</p>
<lb n="0297a23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0297a2301">右此大聖大祕要法。人間希有。實勿傳之宜
<lb n="0297a24" ed="T"/><note n="0297037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">誡＝誠【明】【丙】</note><app n="0297037"><lem wit="【大】">誡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】">誠</rdg></app>慎也。</p>
<lb n="0297a25" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>大聖<note n="0297038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天＝大【明】，〔天〕－【聖】</note><app n="0297038"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">大</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>歡喜雙身毘那夜迦法<note n="0297039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一卷〕－【明】【乙】【丁】</note><app n="0297039"><lem wit="【大】">一<note n="0297040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此下乙本奧書曰己亥之歲卯月十六日以御本交點了　加點了玄胤了，丙本奧書曰文和二年己亥二月二十七日於神護寺成身院書寫訖宣澄二十四歲，丁本奧書曰貞享四年中春十八夕一校點了淨嚴四十九歲元祿十五年十一月二十三日以御本再校了</note>卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>